data.title: DEEEELICIOUS!!
data.text: Thee BEST donuts around.  Nice variety, always fresh!  Owners/staff are very nice and helpful.  Hard to stop in for just one donut, and not buy two!

data.title: Sweet like their name
data.text: My family has always enjoyed our neighborhood donut shop. The owners are friendly and fast. I personally enjoy apple fritters and they serve ones that are larger than most. They also have a good variety of donuts and drinks. I use their shop for treats for our family and when it's my turn to bring treats to work and church.

data.title: Super bons!
data.text: De passage à Los Angeles, nous nous sommes arrêtés dans ce magasin de donuts qui ne payait pas de mine d'extérieur. Et nous avons bien fait car ils étaient excellents, frais énorme et pas cher du tout (1$ le donut gigantesque)! Une super bonne adresse en somme ;) Allez-y!
